lolwut
Class Enemy

java.lang.Object
  lolwut.PhysicalObject
      lolwut.Enemy
Direct Known Subclasses:
FlyingEnemy, WalkingEnemy
public abstract class Enemy
extends PhysicalObject

The abstract class that represents a Lolwut enemy. The basic types of enemies are Kirbeh, Pickatchu, Nian, and Dohmoh.

Author:
Anran Li
